text: Pauline Heßler (born 13 September 1998) is a German ski jumper.. Retrieved 18 February 2018. She has competed at World Cup level since the 2014/15 season, with her best individual result being 18th place in Pyeongchang on 15 February 2017. At the Junior World Championships, she won team gold medals in 2015 and 2017, and team bronze in 2013. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:German female ski jumpers
